CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 26, 1955, pg. A1 reads: "Handsome Pair - Mr. and Mrs. Edward T. Prather following their marriage Nov. 12. The bride is the former Miss Constance Louise Boyd. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of young woman wearing dark short sleeve dress with dark satin bodice, floral lace overlay on shoulders and skirt, and brooch at collar, standing with left hand resting on stomach in interior, possibly Dinwiddie Street, for Prather wedding, Hill District
